high_descs: Head left down the passage and face the table on the left.
Pick up the alarm clock on the table.
Turn right to face the brown shelf.
Put the alarm in the second left shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Put the alarm in the shelf.

high_descs: get away from this room and go straight you can saw a wooden cupboard and turn left and walk towards the table
take the bread toaster beside the other two in the table
turn right you can saw a cupboard on your last right
put a bread toaster in a third shelf of a cupboard
anns.task_desc: put a bread toaster in the third shelf of a cupboard

high_descs: Move left, turn right. Exit to the corridor. Reach the room at the end of the hallway. Cross to the left and then to the right to where the table is.
Pick up the electronic clock that is on the table and then turn right.
Move to the shelf, turn right, left and then right, and put the clock on the second level.
Do not move until further instructions.
anns.task_desc: Move the clock to the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and walk few steps and turn right and walk straight and head towards to the desk in the study room.
At corner turn left and enter the study room.
Turn right and Walk towards to the shelf and get the alarm clock.
Turn right and place the alarm clock on the right side shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the AlarmClock on the Shelf in the study room.

high_descs: Go to the desk near to the shelf.
Take the alarmclock from the table.
Turn right to the shelf side.
Place the alarmclock in the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Take the AlarmClock from the table and place it on the shelf.

high_descs: Leave the room through the door Straight Ahead go into the office and go to the desk.
Pick up the shiny green alarm clock on the desk.
Turn right to the shelf closer to the door.
Place the alarmclock on the second from the bottom left shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place an AlarmClock on the Shelf.
